    "Leveraging LLM's capability to interpret and assign appropriate G-code based on tool specifications for each RA demonstrates the system's potential to manage G-code assignments, demonstrating the capabilities of LLMs.Each product has an LLM-enabled PA which oversees high-level decision-making for its associated product.",
